{"title":"Ai决策与因果推断 .","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Ai决策与因果推断 .","vignette":"%\\VignetteIndexEntry{quarto vignettes} %\\VignetteEncoding{UTF-8} %\\VignetteEngine{quarto::html}\n","knitr":{"opts_chunk":{"collapse":true,"comment":"#>"}},"editor_options":{"chunk_output_type":"console"}},"headingText":"创建数据框","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n**本文主要参考蒋智超老师的「AI是否帮助人类做出更明智的决策？」**\n\n在生活工作中我们常常要做出很多decisions(决策),比如在医疗领域,我们要决定是否给病人做手术,在金融领域,我们要决定是否给某个人贷款,在教育领域,我们要决定是否给某个学生奖学金.这些决策的背后都有一个共同的目标:希望通过干预某个变量X,来改变另一个变量Y的值.比如在医疗领域,我们希望通过给病人做手术来延长他的寿命,在金融领域,我们希望通过给某个人贷款来提高利润,在教育领域,我们希望通过给某个学生奖学金来提高他的学习成绩.在因果推断中,X常常被称为处理(treatment)或干预(intervention),而Y常常被称为结果(outcome).\n\n而在AI高速发展的今天,AI无疑可以帮助我们做出决策,我们可以把决策分为三种:人类独立决策,AI决策,AI辅助决策,各有优劣,如[@tbl-1]所示.\n\n```{r}\n#| label: tbl-1\nlibrary(gt)\n\ndata <- data.frame(\n  Decision_Type = c(\"人类独立决策\", \"AI决策\", \"AI辅助决策\"),\n  Efficiency = c(0,1,1),\n  Consistency = c(1,1,0),\n  Accountability = c(1,1,1)\n)\n\n# 生成表格\ndata %>%\n  gt() %>%\n  cols_label(\n    Decision_Type = \" \",\n    Efficiency = \"高效\",\n    Consistency = \"一致性\",\n    Accountability = \"可追责\"\n  ) %>%\n  tab_options(\n    table.font.size = \"medium\",\n    heading.title.font.size = \"large\",\n    heading.align = \"center\"\n  )\n\n```\n\n\n\n\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n**本文主要参考蒋智超老师的「AI是否帮助人类做出更明智的决策？」**\n\n在生活工作中我们常常要做出很多decisions(决策),比如在医疗领域,我们要决定是否给病人做手术,在金融领域,我们要决定是否给某个人贷款,在教育领域,我们要决定是否给某个学生奖学金.这些决策的背后都有一个共同的目标:希望通过干预某个变量X,来改变另一个变量Y的值.比如在医疗领域,我们希望通过给病人做手术来延长他的寿命,在金融领域,我们希望通过给某个人贷款来提高利润,在教育领域,我们希望通过给某个学生奖学金来提高他的学习成绩.在因果推断中,X常常被称为处理(treatment)或干预(intervention),而Y常常被称为结果(outcome).\n\n而在AI高速发展的今天,AI无疑可以帮助我们做出决策,我们可以把决策分为三种:人类独立决策,AI决策,AI辅助决策,各有优劣,如[@tbl-1]所示.\n\n```{r}\n#| label: tbl-1\nlibrary(gt)\n\n# 创建数据框\ndata <- data.frame(\n  Decision_Type = c(\"人类独立决策\", \"AI决策\", \"AI辅助决策\"),\n  Efficiency = c(0,1,1),\n  Consistency = c(1,1,0),\n  Accountability = c(1,1,1)\n)\n\n# 生成表格\ndata %>%\n  gt() %>%\n  cols_label(\n    Decision_Type = \" \",\n    Efficiency = \"高效\",\n    Consistency = \"一致性\",\n    Accountability = \"可追责\"\n  ) %>%\n  tab_options(\n    table.font.size = \"medium\",\n    heading.title.font.size = \"large\",\n    heading.align = \"center\"\n  )\n\n```\n\n\n\n\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"knitr"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","default-image-extension":"png","to":"html","output-file":"ai.html"},"language":{"toc-title-document":"Table of contents","toc-title-website":"On this page","related-formats-title":"Other Formats","related-notebooks-title":"Notebooks","source-notebooks-prefix":"Source","other-links-title":"Other Links","code-links-title":"Code Links","launch-dev-container-title":"Launch Dev Container","launch-binder-title":"Launch Binder","article-notebook-label":"Article Notebook","not